{"tid":1670575,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"菲律賓、印尼、印度算唔算係hacker及匿名上網者的天堂 ？","createTime":"2019-10-23T04:38:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-23T13:06:39.000Z","uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"f77010e159d68334c9510ea873eaf6e117d66f76","tid":1670575,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T04:38:11.000Z","msg":"全球 IP 地址分佈<br />\n<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/List_of_countries_by_IPv4_address_allocation\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FList_of_countries_by_IPv4_address_allocation&d=6Qw6l1jLXmk45E1e9I%2Bltm8KfKULefuOMk0AcQ9dAAw%3D&h=ec2c876c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/List_of_countries_by_IPv4_address_allocation</a><br />\n<br />\n全球及亞州網民數量<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.internetworldstats.com/stats.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.internetworldstats.com%2Fstats.htm&d=6Qw6l1jLXmk45E1e9I%2Bltm8KfKULefuOMk0AcQ9dAAw%3D&h=dd9ad49d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.internetworldstats.com/stats.htm</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.internetworldstats.com/stats3.htm#asia\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.internetworldstats.com%2Fstats3.htm%23asia&d=6Qw6l1jLXmk45E1e9I%2Bltm8KfKULefuOMk0AcQ9dAAw%3D&h=3048a604\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.internetworldstats.com/stats3.htm#asia</a><br />\n<br />\nIPv6使用量<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com/intl/en/ipv6/statistics.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Fintl%2Fen%2Fipv6%2Fstatistics.html&d=6Qw6l1jLXmk45E1e9I%2Bltm8KfKULefuOMk0AcQ9dAAw%3D&h=0e8ce5e7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com/intl/en/ipv6/statistics.html</a><br />\n<br />\n國家：IP地址（網民數量）<br />\n美國：15億（3.1億網民）<br />\n中國：3.3億（8.5億網民）<br />\n台灣：3538萬（2200萬網民）<br />\n印度：3468萬（5.6億網民）<br />\n香港：1177萬（670萬網民）<br />\n菲律賓：540萬（7900萬網民）<br />\n印尼：1735萬（1.71億網民）<br />\n<br />\n菲律賓、印尼、印度等國家的IP地址嚴重短缺<br />\n意味住基本上係全國都玩共享IP<br />\n一個IP平均有十幾人用緊<br />\n有些可能百幾人用緊<br />\n<br />\n查 IP 通常係警方追查網上記錄和網上犯錯的重要手段。<br />\n如果hacker要hack人地部機，留有ip記錄<br />\n在美國和香港，基本實繼正。<br />\n但在菲律賓、印尼、印度，咁多共享IP，要捉到好難捉到你。<br />\n再加上用匿名IP或暗網技術就更追查。<br />\n原本呢些窮國，已經多hacker想搵食，仲要派咁少IP，完全成就佢地做hacker的天堂。"},{"pid":"d7f36aa21af08b3952e55ccfb240fda301fe3ee2","tid":1670575,"uid":83251,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T12:48:41.000Z","msg":"菲律賓上網好慢，尤其是馬尼拉以外既地方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15be25de634c28898bb20ae9b470997e38e0cb84","tid":1670575,"uid":73741,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T13:06:39.000Z","msg":"BLOCKED"}]}